Lori Heuring https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lori_Heuring 0 Lori Ann Heuring (born April 6, 1973) is a Panamanian/American film and television actress, perhaps most known for her starring role in 8mm 2, as Alice Richards in The Locket (2002), and as Mrs. Kesher in David Lynch's Mulholland Drive (2001).
